<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Irk" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Irk,</orth> impers. vb.; <emph>it --s</emph> == it gives pain, it annoys, it mortifies: <cit><quote>it --s me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it --s his heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.4.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 4, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it --s my very soul,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 6</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>